
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

KeyVault:

* Many resources have secrets like connection strings, secrets...etc and these are stored in configuration files
* Will be easy for hackers to get these keys

* So KeyVault safely stores secrets
* Need AD authentication to access
* Supports Hardware Security models
* Accessed by REST API

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Security Center:

* A central location for monitoring and alerting security related issues
* Shows list of problems found in resources

-------------------------------------------------------------------------